"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月10日消息，MicroStrategy CEO Michael Saylor（迈克尔塞勒）在接受采访时谈到了最近的国会听证会，并认为讨论的最终赢家是[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)。他认为刺激驱动的通胀环境对比特币有利，Saylor称黄金为死石，人们能做的最好的事情就是卖出价值10万亿美元的黄金并购买比特币。12月9日，Saylor发推称，以大约8240万美元现金买入1434枚比特币。（coingape）\",\"timestamp\":1639118495,\"title\":\"MicroStrategy CEO：卖掉黄金并购买比特币是更好的选择\"},\"digest\":\"Z4PhWyjn-Gx9h1UeJPEVh_J0hcgfBygkHNqO64L3h08\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1ecCD624f017532972fF287017A037e7bCf1Dd20\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6AGubF3234IW5cUeug4YDmL498ScJa76U1AaASAoOB8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BVEx2P5votUCgqKlAfUoTLg1vNWNyrPiYEOg8oDVbFQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"fjnHECqx7rbZU4BrpAAVosFSBSva2XuzQOahAMe5GLyim2KY88XYy-asUT4Mp7N0rC5nWjgq9t0kWzo2IrGt8w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb1affe2d7d006f250c5637632b17660828b50a0c8849dd3242542b960b8ec62701ecfe02efef8a3c1633034d3d275217a550b10a281fec85faa5e495111b32201b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6AGubF3234IW5cUeug4YDmL498ScJa76U1AaASAoOB8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BVEx2P5votUCgqKlAfUoTLg1vNWNyrPiYEOg8oDVbFQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Z4PhWyjn-Gx9h1UeJPEVh_J0hcgfBygkHNqO64L3h08\"}"